node.text: As athletes, we rely on our community of teammates and coaches to keep us on top of our game — Shout out to celebrated @oakhillacademy Strength and Conditioning Coaches, @bmeagher22 and @kurtzm3, for showing us that you can still train as a team, even when you’re apart. Tag your training buddy for a quick reminder to #makethedayscount!

node.text: Just a kid from Louisiana to Gatorade Player of the Year to Pro Football Hall of Famer, Peyton Manning’s rise to the Golden Jacket was one only kids would dream of. Congrats on the highest honor in pro football, Sheriff.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Gatorade on August 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and text.

Photo by Gatorade on August 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'DEAR PEYTON CONGRATULATIONS It's been an honor to watch your career unfold. Milestone after milestone, records broken and records set, MVP's, All-Pro teams, Super Bowl wins and now, with the Hall of Fame, you've achieved it all. From Gatorade Player of the Year to Golden Jacket recipient. Congrats on being inducted in the Pro Football Hall of Fame. You've raised the bar, and we're proud to have fueled your journey from Newman to Canton.'.
